posting_body: ['PROP # 01K32', 'MIAMI: 4/2.5', 'Charming 4 bedroom 2.5 bathrooms Townhouse for Rent in the renowned community of Kendall Breeze.', 'This beautiful, updated home features an open floor plan, with ample living areas; the kitchen overlooks the patio and family room, which is ideal for entertaining.', 'It offers lots of closet spaces, 3 bedrooms offers walk-in closets, laundry room is conveniently located upstairs and the garage can be used as a home office.', 'This spacious home is located less than a mile to Turnpike, Miami-Dade College and shopping centers within walking distance.', 'The community is well maintained and features 3 community pools, clubhouse, children’s playground and a gym.', 'Move in ready, fast association approval.', 'Don’t miss this opportunity, make your appointment today!Read Less', 'Rent 1 Sale 1 Kendall', "Bad credit, no credit, come in we'll help you.", '*****', 'Se habla español *****', 'Interested in a property:', 'Call/Text-', 'show contact info', "786'+'7O8'+'2475", 'Call-', 'show contact info', "3O5'+'982'+'8O15", '**R1S1 -Kendall posts properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to current high rental demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, canceled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed**', 'T a g s:', '- Kendall', '- Fontainebleau', '- West Fontainebleau', '- Dadeland']
